Add route:curl -X POST "http://localhost:8080/api/routes?from=Platform%201&to=Platform%202&distanceMeters=80"
List stations:curl http://localhost:8080/api/stations
Get shortest path:curl "http://localhost:8080/api/path?from=Entrance&to=Restroom"
From the project root run:mvn spring-boot:run
Open:

REST API: http://localhost:8080/api

H2 console: http://localhost:8080/h2-console (JDBC URL: jdbc:h2:mem:railwaydb, user sa, empty password)

Optional client: http://localhost:8080/
